				<outline text="&lt;a href=&quot;https://tiddly.packett.cool/&quot;&gt;TiddlyPWA&lt;/a&gt; is a progressive web version of TiddlyWiki. I need to read more about how this works, particularly its synchronization. " created="Tue, 01 Aug 2023 20:19:07 GMT" type="outline"/>
